<h2 id=3D"PaginatingAPIsearchresults-Adapters">Adapters</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Adapter class name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre>eZ\Publish\Core\Pagination\Pagerfanta\Conte=
ntSearchAdapter</pre></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Makes the search against passed Query and return=
s <a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/ezpublish-kernel/blob/master/eZ/P=
ublish/API/Repository/Values/Content/Content.php" class=3D"external-link" r=
el=3D"nofollow">Content</a> objects.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre>eZ\Publish\Core\Pagination\Pa=
gerfanta\ContentSearchHitAdapter</pre></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Same as ContentSearchAdapter but r=
eturns instead <a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/ezpublish-kernel/blo=
b/master/eZ/Publish/API/Repository/Values/Content/Search/SearchHit.php" cla=
ss=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">SearchHit</a> objects.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre>eZ\Publish\Core\Pagination\Pa=
gerfanta\LocationSearchAdapter</pre></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Makes a Location search against pa=
ssed Query and returns Location objects.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre>eZ\Publish\Core\Pagination\Pa=
gerfanta\LocationSearchHitAdapter</pre></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Same as LocationSearchAdapter but =
returns instead <a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/ezpublish-kernel/bl=
ob/master/eZ/Publish/API/Repository/Values/Content/Search/SearchHit.php" cl=
ass=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">SearchHit</a> objects.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
